### 주문 API 테스트

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001/api
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@orderId = YOUR_ORDER_ID_HERE

### 1. 주문 생성 (POST /api/orders)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "items": [
    {
      "product": "PRODUCT_ID_HERE",
      "quantity": 2,
      "selectedSize": "M"
    },
    {
      "product": "ANOTHER_PRODUCT_ID_HERE",
      "quantity": 1,
      "selectedSize": "L"
    }
  ],
  "shippingInfo": {
    "recipientName": "홍길동",
    "recipientPhone": "010-1234-5678",
    "address": "서울시 강남구 테헤란로 123",
    "postalCode": "06234",
    "deliveryRequest": "부재 시 문앞에 놓아주세요"
  },
  "payment": {
    "method": "card"
  }
}

### 2. 내 주문 목록 조회 (GET /api/orders)
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. 주문 상세 조회 (GET /api/orders/:orderId)
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 주문 취소 (PATCH /api/orders/:orderId/cancel)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/cancel
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "cancelReason": "단순 변심"
}

### ============ 관리자 전용 API ============

### 5. 결제 완료 처리 (PATCH /api/orders/:orderId/payment) - 관리자
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/payment
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "transactionId": "TXN-20251112-12345"
}

### 6. 주문 상태 변경 (PATCH /api/orders/:orderId/status) - 관리자
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "status": "preparing"
}

### 7. 배송 시작 (PATCH /api/orders/:orderId/shipping) - 관리자
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/shipping
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "carrier": "CJ대한통운",
  "trackingNumber": "123456789012"
}

### 8. 배송 완료 (PATCH /api/orders/:orderId/delivery) - 관리자
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/delivery
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 9. 모든 주문 조회 (GET /api/orders/admin/all) - 관리자
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/admin/all
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============ 주문 상태 흐름 ============
# pending (주문 생성) 
#   -> confirmed (결제 완료) 
#   -> preparing (배송 준비 중) 
#   -> shipping (배송 중) 
#   -> delivered (배송 완료)
# 
# 또는 cancelled (취소)

